Definition: Whether the "first sentence" and the "second sentence" have the same meaning? Choose one from the option: yes or no.

Positive Examples.input: first sentence: Does Shutterfly ship to Australia? second sentence: Do international students at schools like Ubud use trusted, well-known software for online learning?

first sentence: Which state in India has most beautiful people (men and women) at present? second sentence: Why do we see very attractive and educated females while there are so many good looking and physically fit men?
